description:
This is a 16 minute workout called '15-Minute Walk-Run Intervals | Follow Along Treadmill Workout!' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
